headline: Trimble Announces the SketchUp 0-60 Challenge Winners
summary: Trimble速 (Nasdaq: TRMB) announced the winners of the SketchUp速 0-60 Challenge, an initiative created by Trimble SketchUp and Trimble Ventures to foster innovation and discover the next big idea that will transform how architects, designers and project managers work. The 0-60 Challenge invited entrepreneurs, early-stage startups and developers to leverage SketchUp to develop transformative technology solutions that solve common industry pain points.
